rubric.en:
dist2(P, Q) computes the squared distance from P to Q.

Expected code/algorithm:
cmp(P, Q, R) {
  if (ccw(P, Q, R) > 0) return -1;
  if (ccw(P, Q, R) < 0) return 1;
  d1 = dist2(P, Q);
  d2 = dist2(P, R);
  if (d1 == d2) return 0;
  if (d1 < d2) return -1;
  else return 1;
}

